        <p class="font-body text-on-surface leading-relaxed mb-6">Label each box with a unique barcode or number. Create a spreadsheet linking box IDs to part types, quantities, and locations. Barcode scanners at picking stations speed up order fulfillment and reduce picking errors.</p>

        <h3 class="font-headline text-xl font-bold text-on-surface mb-4">Zone-Based Storage Layout</h3>
        <p class="font-body text-on-surface leading-relaxed mb-6">Organize the warehouse into zones (Zone A for high-turnover parts, Zone B for medium, Zone C for slow-moving). Place used boxes strategically so pickers can grab items quickly without traversing the entire warehouse.</p>

        <h3 class="font-headline text-xl font-bold text-on-surface mb-4">FIFO Rotation System</h3>
        <p class="font-body text-on-surface leading-relaxed mb-6">Implement First-In-First-Out (FIFO) rotation to prevent obsolescence and damage. Use colored stickers or date labels on boxes to track aging components and ensure fresher stock moves out first.</p>

